section.para:
Below is a very simple named.conf, in our example
  environment, this file is /etc/bind/named.conf. The
  lines you most likely need to add are in bold.

   options {
    dnssec-enable yes;
    directory "/etc/bind";
    recursion no;
    minimal-responses yes;
};

zone "example.com" IN {
    type master;
    file "db/example.com.db";
    key-directory "keys/example.com";
    inline-signing yes;
    auto-dnssec maintain;
};
